Class MovieListing

  • java.lang.Object
    • MovieListing
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<MovieListing>

    public class MovieListing
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<MovieListing>
    A MovieListing represents a particular showtime of a Movie. It holds attributes such as movie title, listingCode (unique identifier), location and time information.

    SS3 Group 6
